    </a>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td valign="top" align="left">
		<font face="verdana" size="2">
		<b>Description:</b> <br>
		This should be used against any mob who use magic spells against you. Cast this spell to slow/stop a mob from casting.<BR>
<BR>
<B>Location:</B><BR>Pg.90 Sali's
		</font>
	 </td>
	 <td rowspan="4" valign="top" align="right">
    
