				50+ Fighting.. I'm 55 and use Theft of Thought+Wandering Mind+Mana Sieve. I take their mana and then keep casting Sieve. Keeps the Caster Sebilis froggies without mana to gate and intrupts them. All they have left is weakling arms to try and fight.. You can reduce damage to your team this way. Works wonders. Dazzle 1 Dazzle 2 Dazzle 3 Dazzle 4; sit count of 10sec; Theft 1 Dazzle 1, Dazzle 2 wander 2, Dazzle 3 Dazzle 4;sit count ten &gt;throw in sieve to one being fought inbetween some where. Dazzle does work with some resist's but it last's long time. AOE Facination is to quickly mez a mob of npc's and you dont know which the Main Assist will attack. It doesnt last long enough for medding or doing much else but will save your behind. After your down to 3 to mez, use dazzle as they break. Warn your cleric to cover you while you get hit on til you get them dazzled. then time your re-dazzles to allow medding or casting to assist the fight. Some enchanters like to Chain Stun with color slant series, that I find can aggro and get resisted. I just like to dazzle so i can med. If I have 2 dazzled, i can actually gain mana with the theft series and make casters empty with seive thrown in.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
